{
  "name": "ColorStops",
  "summary": "<p>每个 <strong>ColorStop</strong> 对象代表一个区域或选定内容中渐变填充的一个颜色光圈。</p>\n<p><b class=\"mainheaders\">示例</b></p><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*以下示例显示了具有线性渐变的颜色停止。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> interior = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Selection</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Interior</span>\n    interior.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Pattern</span> = xlPatternLinearGradient\n    interior.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Gradient</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Degree</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">90</span>\n    interior.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Gradient</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ColorStops</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Clear</span>()\n\n    <span class=\"hljs-comment\">//adds stops after any have been cleared</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> colorStops1 = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Selection</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Interior</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Gradient</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ColorStops</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Add</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>)\n    colorStops1.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ThemeColor</span> = xlThemeColorDark1\n    colorStops1.<span class=\"hljs-property\">TintAndShade</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>\n\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> colorStops2 = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Selection</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Interior</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Gradient</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ColorStops</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Add</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    colorStops2.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ThemeColor</span> = xlThemeColorAccent1\n    colorStops2.<span class=\"hljs-property\">TintAndShade</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*以下示例显示了具有矩形渐变的颜色停止点。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> interior = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Selection</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Interior</span>\n    interior.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Pattern</span> = xlPatternRectangularGradient\n    interior.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Gradient</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">RectangleLeft</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>\n    interior.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Gradient</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">RectangleRight</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>\n    interior.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Gradient</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">RectangleTop</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>\n    interior.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Gradient</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">RectangleBottom</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>\n    interior.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Gradient</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ColorStops</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Clear</span>()\n\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> colorStops1 = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Selection</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Interior</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Gradient</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ColorStops</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Add</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>)\n    colorStops1.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Color</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">192</span>\n    colorStops1.<span class=\"hljs-property\">TintAndShade</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>\n\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> colorStops2 = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Selection</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Interior</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Gradient</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ColorStops</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Add</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    colorStops2.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ThemeColor</span> = xlThemeColorLight1\n    colorStops2.<span class=\"hljs-property\">TintAndShade</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
  "description": "<p>指定的数据系列中所有 ColorStop 对象的集合。</p>\n",
  "category": "et",
  "properties": [
    {
      "name": "Count",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回指定对象的计数。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*以下示例显示活动单元格中的 ColorStops 数。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveCell</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Interior</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Gradient</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ColorStops</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Count</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "number（int4 精度）",
      "readonly": true
    }
  ],
  "functions": [
    {
      "name": "Add",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>将一个 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/ColorStop/ColorStop .htm#ColorStop.ColorStop\">ColorStop</a></strong> 对象添加到指定集合。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*为当前选定区域添加一个ColorStop。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1:A10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Select</span>()\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> colorStop = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Selection</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Interior</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Gradient</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ColorStops</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Add</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    colorStop.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ThemeColor</span> = xlThemeColorAccent1\n    colorStop.<span class=\"hljs-property\">TintAndShade</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例为活动单元格添加一个ColorStop，并将主题颜色设置为xlThemeColorDark2。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> colorStop = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveCell</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Interior</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Gradient</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ColorStops</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Add</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">0.5</span>)\n    colorStop.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ThemeColor</span> = xlThemeColorDark2\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "parameters": [
        {
          "name": "Position",
          "type": "number（double 精度）",
          "description": "<p>代表要应用 <strong>ColorStop</strong> 的位置。</p>\n",
          "optional": false
        }
      ],
      "returns": "<p>ColorStop</p>\n"
    },
    {
      "name": "Clear",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>清除指定对象。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例清除选定区域当前 ColorStops。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1:A10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Select</span>()\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> interior = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Selection</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Interior</span>\n    interior.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Pattern</span> = xlPatternLinearGradient\n    interior.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Gradient</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Degree</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">90</span>\n    interior.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Gradient</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ColorStops</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Clear</span>()\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例清除活动单元格当前 ColorStops。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveCell</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Interior</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Gradient</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ColorStops</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Clear</span>()\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "parameters": [],
      "returns": "<p>void</p>\n"
    },
    {
      "name": "Item",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>从指定集合中返回单个对象。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例删除活动单元格第三个ColorStop对象。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> colorStop = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveCell</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Interior</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Gradient</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ColorStops</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>)\n    colorStop.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Delete</span>()\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将当前选定区域的第一个ColorStop对象的TintAndShade属性设置为-1。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1:A10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Select</span>()\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> colorStop = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Selection</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Interior</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Gradient</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ColorStops</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    colorStop.<span class=\"hljs-property\">TintAndShade</span> = -<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "parameters": [
        {
          "name": "Index",
          "type": "any",
          "description": "<p>对象的名称或索引号。</p>\n",
          "optional": false
        }
      ],
      "returns": "<p>一个包含在集合中的 <strong>ColorStops</strong> 对象。</p>\n"
    }
  ]
